"title": "6667: grace, in OT",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6667",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>In the OT, grace is evident in the special relationship between God and his people.</p>\n<h2>God's grace was expressed in the covenant relationship</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:7-Deut7:9\">DEU 7:7–7:9</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs13:22-2Kgs13:23\">2KI 13:22–13:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen9:8-Gen9:11\">GEN 9:8–9:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen17:1-Gen17:8\">GEN 17:1–17:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod6:2-Exod6:8\">EXO 6:2–6:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:17-Deut8:18\">DEU 8:17–8:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh1:5-Neh1:6\">NEH 1:5–1:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:1-Isa55:3\">ISA 55:1–55:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:1-Ezek16:8\">EZK 16:1–16:8</a></p>\n<h2>God's grace affirmed</h2>\n<h3>God's grace shown in his compassion</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps86:15\">PSA 86:15</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:22\">LAM 3:22</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:13\">JOL 2:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod33:19\">EXO 33:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut13:17-Deut13:18\">DEU 13:17–13:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr30:9\">2CH 30:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra8:22\">EZR 8:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:13\">PSA 103:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek39:25\">EZK 39:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos2:19\">HOS 2:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah4:1-Jonah4:2\">JON 4:1–4:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic7:18-Mic7:20\">MIC 7:18–7:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech10:6\">ZEC 10:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:17\">MAL 3:17</a></p>\n<h3>God's grace shown in his readiness to forgive</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:7\">ISA 55:7</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer33:6-Jer33:9\">JER 33:6–33:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan9:9-Dan9:10\">DAN 9:9–9:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic7:18-Mic7:20\">MIC 7:18–7:20</a></p>\n<h3>God's grace shown in his favour, provision and healing</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:9\">LEV 26:9</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:40-Jer32:41\">JER 32:40–32:41</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num10:29\">NUM 10:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut13:17-Deut13:18\">DEU 13:17–13:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:28\">2SA 22:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps30:4-Ps30:5\">PSA 30:4–30:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:8\">ISA 49:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:23-Jer9:24\">JER 9:23–9:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer33:6-Jer33:9\">JER 33:6–33:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah1:7\">NAM 1:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech12:10\">ZEC 12:10</a></p>\n<h2>God made his grace known to individuals</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:16-Neh9:20\">NEH 9:16–9:20</a></strong> <em>The Israelites confess their sins</em>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job10:12\">JOB 10:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:35-Gen24:36\">GEN 24:35–24:36</a> <em>Abraham</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen32:9-Gen32:10\">GEN 32:9–32:10</a> <em>Jacob</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen39:20-Gen39:21\">GEN 39:20–39:21</a> <em>Joseph</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod33:12-Exod33:13\">EXO 33:12–33:13</a> <em>Moses</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut33:23\">DEU 33:23</a> <em>Naphtali</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg2:18\">JDG 2:18</a> <em>in the period of the judges</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:21\">1SA 2:21</a> <em>Hannah</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:6\">1KI 3:6</a> <em>Solomon</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra7:27-Ezra7:28\">EZR 7:27–7:28</a> <em>Ezra</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh2:8\">NEH 2:8</a> <em>Nehemiah</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps6:9\">PSA 6:9</a> <em>David</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:10\">ISA 26:10</a> <em>God's grace may be unavailing.</em></p>\n<h2>God's grace implored</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr33:12\">2CH 33:12</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps51:1\">PSA 51:1</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa33:2\">ISA 33:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:12\">GEN 24:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod32:11\">EXO 32:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:28-1Kgs8:30\">1KI 8:28–8:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs13:4\">2KI 13:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:32\">NEH 9:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps25:16\">PSA 25:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps69:13\">PSA 69:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan9:17-Dan9:19\">DAN 9:17–9:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos14:2\">HOS 14:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab3:2\">HAB 3:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech1:12\">ZEC 1:12</a></p>",
